    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed at this model risk level. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. High assurance level declared based on comprehensive factor coverage and favorable validation outcomes across primary operating points. Velocity field and pressure-head validations provide additional confidence beyond minimum requirements.",
